      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. While the engine and transmission are reliable and it remains mechanically sound for regular use, there are some visible signs of age. You can expect some cosmetic wear on the interior upholstery and a few minor dents and paint chips on the exterior. Additionally, a few non-essential electronic features are currently intermittent, and the suspension may need a refresh in the near future. It is a solid, functional car that is priced to reflect its current state and the maintenance it will eventually require.",
