      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that\u2019s ready for the road? This well-loved vehicle is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who values function over perfection! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a dependable choice that still has plenty of life left. It\u2019s the perfect budget-friendly option for someone looking for a solid ride with character!",
